      "instruction": "Rinse all 12x75mm Fisher culture tubes needed for experimentwith 1mL MeOH, vortex for 2sec, dump MeOH waste into waste beaker, add another1mL MeOH to each tube, vortex for 2 sec, dump MeOH into waste and placeinverted tubes in tube rack in drying oven at 60C",
